item.title: XY Utilities v1.1.0.6
item.description:
Product: XY Utilities v1.1.0.6
Company: LevyLab
Release Date: Tue, 12 May 2020 16:20:38 -0400
Packager: Patrick Irvin

Description: Utilities for working with XY-data type (Cluster of 1D X and Y arrays).

Supported methods:
- Arithmetic: Add, Subtract, Multiply, Divide
- Array: Sort, Reverse, Decimate, Subset, Sway X and Y, Get X and Y, Append, Waveform to XY
- DSP: Derivative, Average, Interpolate, Resample, FFT Spectrum, FFT Power Spectrum

Release Notes: [1.1.0.6]
New methods:
- Interpolate Parameter.vi: interpolate along "parameter" dimension
- Interpolate Y.vi: for a given x value interpolate and return a fractional Y value
- Shift Zero.vi: adjust zero value for a given fractional x index (useful for magnetic field sweeps)
Bug Fixes:
- Interpolate.vi: now also interpolates the x array
item.dc:creator: LevyLab

item.title: Multichannel Lockin v2.9.11.19
item.description:
Product: Multichannel Lockin v2.9.11.19
Company: LevyLab
Release Date: Thu, 09 Apr 2020 13:55:17 -0400
Packager: Patrick Irvin

Description: Multichannel Lockin for National Instruments' Dynamic Signal Acquisition hardware (4431, 4461, 4462). This version is configured to handle multiple cards for simultaneous, synchronized AI/AO. You can configure a number of analog outputs (up to 8) to output sine, square, sawtooth, or triangle functions with DC offsets. Each of the analog inputs (up to 8) can be demodulated at multiple frequencies.

Release Notes: [2.9.11.19]
- Build version automatically updated on front panel
- Remove LVtoIBW from package dependencies
item.dc:creator: LevyLab
